          Default table cell
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <code>&lt;th&gt;</code>
        </td>
        <td>
          Special table cell for column (or row, depending on scope and placement) labels
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <code>&lt;caption&gt;</code>
        </td>
        <td>
          Description or summary of what the table holds, especially useful for screen readers
        </td>
      </tr>
